<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>BloomHub Blog</title>

  <!-- SEO -->
  <meta name="description" content="BloomHub Blog - Plant care guides, gardening tips, and inspiration for plant lovers.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="blog, gardening tips, indoor plants, outdoor plants, plant care">
  <meta name="author" content="BloomHub">
  <link rel="icon" href="<%= '/images/favicon.ico' %>" />

  <!-- CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= '/css/blog.css' %>" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

  <style>
    /* Blog Page Styling */

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background: #f9fdf9;
      color: #333;
    }

    header.blog-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #2f6d2f, #4caf50);
      color: #fff;
    }

    header.blog-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    header.blog-header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    nav.blog-categories {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      padding: 15px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    nav.blog-categories a {
      padding: 8px 18px;
      border: 1px solid #2f6d2f;
      border-radius: 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #2f6d2f;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    nav.blog-categories a:hover {
      background: #2f6d2f;
      color: #fff;
    }

    main.blog-main {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 3fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    section.blog-list h2 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #2f6d2f;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .grid article {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .grid article:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .grid img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 180px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .grid h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin: 10px;
      color: #2f6d2f;
    }

    .grid p {
      margin: 0 10px 15px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    aside.blog-sidebar {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    aside.blog-sidebar h3 {
      color: #2f6d2f;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    aside.blog-sidebar ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    aside.blog-sidebar ul li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    aside.blog-sidebar form {
      display: flex;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    aside.blog-sidebar input {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px;
    }

    aside.blog-sidebar button {
      background: #2f6d2f;
      border: none;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    section.blog-footer-cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      background: #eaf7ea;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    section.blog-footer-cta h2 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #2f6d2f;
    }

    section.blog-footer-cta .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: #2f6d2f;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    section.blog-footer-cta .cta-btn:hover {
      background: #4caf50;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Blog Header -->
  <header class="blog-header">
    <h1>🌱 BloomHub Blog</h1>
    <p>Your go-to guide for plant care, gardening tips, and inspiration.</p>
  </header>

  <!-- Blog Categories -->
  <nav class="blog-categories">
    <a href="/blog/indoor">Indoor Plants</a>
    <a href="/blog/outdoor">Outdoor Plants</a>
    <a href="/blog/tools">Gardening Tools</a>
    <a href="/blog/tips">Tips & Guides</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- Blog Content -->
  <main class="blog-main">
    <!-- Blog Articles -->
    <section class="blog-list">
      <h2>Latest Articles</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <article>
          <a href="https://www.architecturaldigest.com/story/how-to-care-for-succulents" style="text-decoration: none;">
            <img src="<%= '/images/care.jpg' %>" alt="Succulent Care" />
            <h3>How to Care for Succulents</h3>
            <p>Succulents are low-maintenance, but they need proper sunlight and watering. Learn the do's and don'ts.</p>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article>
          <a href="https://phsonline.org/for-gardeners/gardeners-blog/15-common-houseplants-perfect-for-your-home" style="text-decoration: none;">
            <img src="<%= '/images/tenplants.jpg' %>" alt="Indoor Plants" />
            <h3>15 Best Indoor Plants</h3>
            <p>Greenery that fits perfectly in your living room while purifying air.</p>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article>
          <a href="https://www.ugaoo.com/collections/garden-tools?srsltid=AfmBOoqoaws_WDVm1LvmLdzgeEXHTP47yxh884bXhfjfT6AAnL7h27ox" style="text-decoration: none;">
            <img src="<%= '/images/gardeningtools.jpg' %>" alt="Gardening Tools" />
            <h3>Essential Gardening Tools</h3>
            <p>Everything you need to start your garden journey hassle-free.</p>
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <aside class="blog-sidebar">
      <h3>🌿 Quick Tips</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Water plants in the morning for better absorption.</li>
        <li>Rotate pots weekly for even sunlight.</li>
        <li>Use compost for healthier soil.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>📩 Subscribe</h3>
      <form action="/subscribe" method="post">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email" required />
        <button type="submit">Join</button>
      </form>
    </aside>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer CTA -->
  <section class="blog-footer-cta">
    <h2>Want More Green Inspiration?</h2>
    <p>Check out our plant shop or explore more guides!</p>
    <a href="/" class="cta-btn">Back to Home</a>
  </section>
</body>

</html>
